shipper to determine exactly what that is.

30:19.820 --> 30:21.620
It's used in the manufacture of glue.

30:21.660 --> 30:23.180
Can you hold on one moment?

30:24.420 --> 30:26.620
- You know what is phenol?
- Yes.

30:29.140 --> 30:31.620
Uh... Mr Galvin, we have a
