31:09.900 --> 31:12.420
- All right, I'll be ready.
- You will not be on the call, Ms. Hooper.

31:13.180 --> 31:15.100
- Excuse me?
- You will be advised.

31:15.300 --> 31:17.020
We now coordinate with local authorities.

31:17.500 --> 31:20.300
God knows, we have more than 100
crossings that need to be secured.

31:20.660 --> 31:23.780
