Now!

59:22.580 --> 59:25.460
Open fire! Open fire!
Damn!

59:25.500 --> 59:26.980
Open fire!

59:27.260 --> 59:31.740
We were aiming at the same level, by firing
shotgun rounds at the fuel stop safety switch.

59:31.780 --> 59:33.660
And So ... some shots were fired.

59:33.740 --> 59:36.500
That safety switch is a mighty small target

59:36.620 --> 59:38.980
and, it's right nex to a fuel tank.

