We're not going to catch him before Arklow.

59:45.580 --> 59:47.260
Frank, you're closing the gap.

59:47.380 --> 59:50.780
You should cut your speed, allow
yourself some stopping distance, just in case.

59:51.220 --> 59:54.060
No can do, Connie.
If we slow down now, we'll never catch him.

59:54.100 --> 59:55.420
Not before Stanton.
Over.

59:55.420 --> 59:56.540
It's your call.

