01:00:05.100 --> 01:00:06.740
It is unclear what's their plan ...

01:00:06.860 --> 01:00:08.260
Connie Hooper for you.

01:00:08.900 --> 01:00:11.860
Did I or did I not tell you
to get 1206 off the Main?

01:00:12.300 --> 01:00:13.940
I asked them nicely.
...This is impossible!

01:00:19.980 --> 01:00:23.460
- You're 100 % sure that derailer won'twork?
