And if it does?

01:00:32.420 --> 01:00:35.540
If does ... then we're
a wreck on a wreck.

01:00:37.540 --> 01:00:40.420
I'am with engineer Jim Deveroux.
The train is getting close.

01:00:40.540 --> 01:00:41.500
How will this derailer work?

