Well, basically, it works like a ramp.

01:00:44.860 --> 01:00:48.380
Train comes along, this piece here,
will lift the flange

01:00:48.420 --> 01:00:50.020
and and pull it outside the rail.

01:00:50.140 --> 01:00:53.900
That will cause the train
to flip over on its right hand side.

01:00:53.980 --> 01:00:55.980
Son of a bitch won't even know...

01:01:31.420 --> 01:01:33.860
What ... What in the hell was that?

01:01:33.940 --> 01:01:37.860
That ... was 10 million pounds of train,
Mr Galvin.

01:01:38.020 --> 01:01:40.220
And, this is the sound of me
saving your ass.

01:01:41.020 --> 01:01:42.260
Frank, do you copy?

01:01:42.740 --> 01:01:45.540
- Frank?
- 1206. Over.

01:01:45.820 --> 01:01:47.580
You were right.

01:01:49.260 --> 01:01:50.780
Jesus Christ!

