The particulars are still
being examined, but

01:02:08.860 --> 01:02:10.380
authorities are far more focused

01:02:10.460 --> 01:02:13.980
on the potential destruction that would
result if train 777

01:02:14.020 --> 01:02:16.620
were to derail in Stanton.

01:02:21.140 --> 01:02:22.860
What did you mean
about being married once?

01:02:24.780 --> 01:02:26.700
Alice, my wife ...she died of cancer.

01:02:27.180 --> 01:02:29.100
- Four years ago.
- Sorry.

01:02:29.380 --> 01:02:30.740
Me too ...

01:02:31.540 --> 01:02:32.860
Me too.

01:02:34.940 --> 01:02:36.500
Every night I come home,

01:02:36.780 --> 01:02:38.620
tell her about my day ...

01:02:38.780 --> 01:02:40.180
where I had been ...

01:02:40.700 --> 01:02:42.060
what I hauled.

01:02:44.540 --> 01:02:46.460
Who annoyed me.

01:02:47.100 --> 01:02:50.300
- You can offend someone?
- You'd be amazed.

01:02:52.700 --> 01:02:54.260
You should call your wife.

01:02:55.100 --> 01:02:57.980
I would but ... but it's her day off.
She's probably sleeping.

01:02:58.100 --> 01:02:59.900
Don't make excuses. Wake her up.

01:03:01.060 --> 01:03:04.060
I called her for the past 2 weeks,
but she never called me back.

01:03:04.140 --> 01:03:06.660
She won't. You got to call her,
that's how it works.

01:03:07.020 --> 01:03:08.500
You quit too easy.

01:03:14.140 --> 01:03:15.660
Stanton, Pennsylvania.

01:03:15.700 --> 01:03:16.820
Darcy!

01:03:18.140 --> 01:03:19.100
Darcy.

01:03:20.860 --> 01:03:23.340
I've been calling...
and calling.

01:03:25.260 --> 01:03:26.420
What is wrong?

01:03:26.500 --> 01:03:28.340
As we told you earlier today,

01:03:28.420 --> 01:03:31.780
those emergency evacuations
began early this morning.

01:03:31.940 --> 01:03:34.020
As they try to move people out of
harms way.

